{"tid":116703,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同另一半識左一陣就一齊既你地 入黎分享下","createTime":"2017-02-11T15:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T17:44:32.000Z","uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd7312ee14cb51a6ddf70c40b182a674e0bad06","tid":116703,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"有無人係識左一陣 例如一星期 就一齊左<br />\n而又拍左好耐拖?<br />\n分享下呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如點解咁快一齊 唔驚未了解晒佢個人咩?"},{"pid":"735205c8183d9ae6af90597254189b30d0f57bc4","tid":116703,"uid":25569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"同佢同班左一年<br />\n本身無乜溝通 無講過野<br />\n突然佢snapchat我 之後瘋狂傾<br />\n<br />\n大家都feel到對大家都有野 就不自然地一齊<br />\n<br />\n正確D講係因為岩timing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606ad68b5221ac606506c8b65af06798d1963d48","tid":116703,"uid":29247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:20:05.000Z","msg":"識左兩個禮拜就拍拖<br />\n拍左六年未分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d0b891abb7368adf3df484dd48c21e5ac8a97b","tid":116703,"uid":9856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"我上年同初戀識左2星期就一齊  不過已散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95d18da05a2a17a80253ba09542c19af1c5e5b3","tid":116703,"uid":42048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"同EX一開始都叫知道大家嘅存在但冇單獨傾過計<br />\nwhatsapp傾左幾日就一齊<br />\n後尾先發覺佢脾氣好差,少少事就會屌人咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dd112c7e29127a96e8ccbb90c6fe5b70198b49","tid":116703,"uid":4382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:44:32.000Z","msg":"同現仼識咗10日到就已經feel到互相有好感<br />\n之後就一齊咗啦<br />\n到依家拍咗年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得拍拖唔洗點追 係鐘意嘅好快就會一齊到